main event: On 13 November 1961, objects were observed passing quickly through the sky for 2 minutes and 30 seconds.
interesting points: The sighting included objects that were gliding silently at the top of trees., The observer noted the presence of a bright object which they believed was a UFO., The report was part of the Project Blue Book investigation into UFO sightings., The report concluded that there was insufficient data for evaluation., There were sketches included in the report but no actual photographs.
